{"tid":469831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超：根據警例緊急情況下查看手機毋須搜查令","createTime":"2017-11-15T17:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T11:31:33.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"7f5173965d44915cb7523f201d138dd75d10a226","tid":469831,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510739625_fbec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510739625_fbec.jpg&h=7a67994c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高等法院較早前裁決警方須有搜查令才可查閱市民手機內資料。保安局局長李家超書面回覆議員提問時表示，警方與律政司現正研究相關判詞，以評估其影響及跟進工作。<br />\n<br />\n但李家超強調，根據判詞，警務人員可根據《警隊條例》第 50（6）條，在被捕人士身上及現場或附近檢取手提電話，而在緊急情況下，警員可以毋須獲得搜查令而查看這些手提電話的電子內容，做法是符合《香港人權法案條例》第14條和《基本法》第30條的規定。"},{"pid":"0fe199b3e9e56e5b61b0a00fe98479d7afbf7841","tid":469831,"uid":76776,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:23:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"305ddc16146290de7d50e584d14c356035860c34","tid":469831,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"在被捕人士身上<br />\n<br />\n以後係咪都拘捕左人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92806c6ad501b342d167f21c6486d4deac61ebae","tid":469831,"uid":19725,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"呢d傻9 都做局長 點解寒戰講到咁難先做到？"},{"pid":"0bd050c1c03ef01a9bfd9dfcf7bc4ac1f10be4e8","tid":469831,"uid":19141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>緊急情況定義係乜?<br />\n我好火緊要睇你D閃卡打丁?</blockquote><br />\n(6)<br />\nWhere any person is apprehended by a police officer it shall be lawful for such officer to search for and take possession of any newspaper, book or other document or any portion or extract therefrom and any other article or chattel which may be found on his person or in or about the place at which he has been apprehended and which the <span style=\"color: red;\">said officer may reasonably suspect </span>to be of value (whether by itself or together with anything else) to the investigation of any offence that the person has committed or is reasonably suspected of having committed:<br />\nProvided that nothing in this subsection shall be construed in diminution of the powers of search conferr"},{"pid":"03d1b4c3b4ad80508cb1b85a9ca97fd8486536b3","tid":469831,"uid":9694,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d傻9 都做局長 點解寒戰講到咁難先做到？</blockquote><br />\n好似出面請人咁<br />\n對外要求高學歷經驗多等等<br />\n識人介紹既小學畢業冇經驗都做到"},{"pid":"4f5256b34b2ccfc6c36a65ce9cc93e0738b19cc3","tid":469831,"uid":93784,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:33:21.000Z","msg":"緊急情況真係任佢講<br />\n香港就係比好多呢D人治概念去管治 無得唔腐爛啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a9772b239578b90e78acc1f308a5a0709c0904","tid":469831,"uid":49392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:13:24.000Z","msg":"咁加定密碼，但到時可能俾人嚇到唔記得咗，你慢慢解，但錯多過四次就會洗機"},{"pid":"0f96228beec351145d27950203aa70c431fc502f","tid":469831,"uid":21035,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T22:14:54.000Z","msg":"警例關我鳩事咩？<br />\n<br />\n而家警例大定法庭大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5768523127a696ccf96e0063905ab7e27e91c89a","tid":469831,"uid":57462,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T22:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警例關我鳩事咩？<br />\n<br />\n而家警例大定法庭大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2017 仲問呢個問題？<br />\n梗係法庭大啦！不過個法官個位就紅底既"},{"pid":"234d6f500499d5b152ad7047c105a44f781b4f24","tid":469831,"uid":38049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T22:37:57.000Z","msg":"出搜查令要證據，我懷疑你就講心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/